Pre-Game Insights: Azerbaijan and Sweden meet in a UEFA Nations League C clash in Baku on September 5, 2024.
Azerbaijan aims to improve from a recent friendly win, while Sweden seeks a strong start after failing to qualify for the European Championships.
Swedish players include Alexander Isak, fresh from a Premier League goal against Tottenham.
Azerbaijan's possible starting lineup features Musa Gurbanly and Mahir Emreli.
